2.  Programming environment included:
    -SelectCtrl
    -Backup
    -Restore
    -Manipulate users information
    -Manage Security Permission
    -Report Library
    -SMS Library
    -Email Library
    -Chart

3. Module shall not effect existing xoops framework
4. Universal php function or javascript shall prepare for others project usage
